                "markdown": "**Vulnerability CVE-2026-28389**\n| Severity | Package | Version | Fix Version | Type | Location | Data Namespace | Link |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| high  | libcrypto3  | 3.6.1-r1  | 3.6.2-r0  | apk  | /usr/lib/apk/db/installed  | wolfi:distro:wolfi:rolling  | [CVE-2026-28389](https://images.chainguard.dev/security/CVE-2026-28389)  |\n"
